body_html: @MacwinWin, if you want to be able to use TRT4.0RC you need to recompile TensorFlow. However we are still working on TRT4.0 support in interface layer so not all features of TRT4 will be available to you. TRT4.0 support in Tensorflow will be available after TensorRT4.0 is released.
